{"tid":2373815,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[原諒者Forgiver]《最後生還者 2 》總監表示有意製作《制裁者》與《惡靈戰警》的電玩遊戲？","createTime":"2021-01-20T18:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T05:16:45.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e734381c24119ec80bad890c5603fc2129790975","tid":2373815,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T18:10:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.toy-people.com/?p=59075&amp;fbclid=IwAR39tuNKU0HbdzJT96wIQ4R0mc2jksUlj20PLKqFr8IhXxFwZ3BFABv_G-8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.toy-people.com%2F%3Fp%3D59075%26fbclid%3DIwAR39tuNKU0HbdzJT96wIQ4R0mc2jksUlj20PLKqFr8IhXxFwZ3BFABv_G-8&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia7is81FSeaDeH2Oz4vdBzj8%3D&h=42648667\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.toy-people.com/?p=59075&amp;fbclid=IwAR39tuNKU0HbdzJT96wIQ4R0mc2jksUlj20PLKqFr8IhXxFwZ3BFABv_G-8</a><br />\n<br />\n褒貶不一的頑皮狗工作室 2020 年度「鉅」作《最後生還者 2 ( The Last of Us Part II )》自發售前就話題不斷。諸如工作室副總，同時也是該遊戲製作總監 Neil Druckmann 的「不爽不要買」風波以及因為玩家反響過於劇烈而導致國外網站禁止「洗負評歪風」等不勝枚舉的事件，然而最近 Neil Druckmann 又大發豪語的表示工作室的下個遊戲目標將放在...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/161114736737.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F161114736737.jpg&h=f104eef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是滴你沒看錯！據本人在推特接受 Greg Miller 提問時表示，他強烈希望能為漫威知名的反英雄《制裁者 The Punisher 》與《惡靈戰警 Ghost Rider 》「量身打造」電玩遊戲，詳見推特連結，而被點名的對象也包含了在美國大受好評的日本動畫《星際牛仔 Cowboy Bebop》！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.toy-people.com/member/161114827821.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.toy-people.com%2Fmember%2F161114827821.jpg&h=ac40ee27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說回來，《制裁者》自從 2020 年 11 月起就沒有新的漫畫連載，最近又因為美國白宮的示威風波而受到影響，再加上 Neil Druckmann 的這番言論，真的只能用「雪上加霜」來形容...<br />\n<br />\n言歸正傳，自 2009 年 PS3 的《 The Punisher: No Mercy 》迄今，《制裁者》的電玩改編近乎「乏人問津」，或許 Neil Druckmann 這次的「發聲」，能讓更多人開始注意這個值得討論的反英雄也說不定？"},{"pid":"e2fc5aebdeefbb43d7b34b12b643f903ca8dafb7","tid":2373815,"uid":165711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T18:15:05.000Z","msg":"想搞half life<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a4d1d95402c203c8aa8881b512730342ab1c6e","tid":2373815,"uid":37666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T18:17:46.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3437464487edf46bde985b5fd2fd8534c0e0c0ca","tid":2373815,"uid":196860,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T05:16:45.000Z","msg":"COWBOY BEBOP 女神FAYE變女猩猩我屌你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}